Players have such varied opinions that I no longer want to hear about it. Here is a very cool GDformosa Super Strat with some nice upgrades. This one was made in Taiwan. If you are not familiar with products made in Taiwan they have an excellent reputation,maybe better than Korean made. Has all black hardware,24 fret maple/rosewood neck with near zero fret wear. Has a small nick to the finish at the tip of the headstock that has been touched up. Otherwise guitar looks very nice with just mild surface scratches. Guitar is completely original except for the electronics . When I bought this guitar the original pickups were not included so I installed two rail type humbuckers in the neck and middle position and a full size HMV Zebra humbucker at the bridge. I also added a push/pull tone control so that the humbuckers can be split into single coils. This gives you 10 different pickup combinations along with the 5 way switch. All electronics work perfectly,and sound great on every setting,clean or with some distortion. No joke these pickups sound killer on this guitar. The capacitor has been upgraded with a Orange Drop style epoxy film capacitor . More range of tone control and a smoother response. A very sexy looking guitar,great colors. Looks,and sounds great.
